{"title":"迎接灿烂的和平之光","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接灿烂的和平之光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（日）池田大作  赵琼译  卞立强校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空有鸟儿飞翔之路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海洋有鱼儿畅游之途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然肉眼难辨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球磁场的感应波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贯穿整个宇宙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管肉眼看不见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命本身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有着俨然存在的法则"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们前进的大道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使谁也看不见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我深信那是空前光荣的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽满鲜花之路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们快长成大树吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝叶繁茂，开出幸福胜利之花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结满累累丰硕之果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿变成人们看不见的树根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深扎入大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们去建造宏伟的大厦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人类和未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿做它坚固的基石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你们携手并肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设新的世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们一定不会辜负我的期望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们结成信赖的纽带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚不可摧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的希望———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的灿烂之光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类步入其他天体的时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这弹丸般小小的地球上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必相互纷争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类都应该是朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该是兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地、海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都充满了生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋溢着孕育万物的慈爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里不必有边境线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个地球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们共同拥有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类合作开发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会更加昌盛繁荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断过去的恶梦吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敞开我们的胸怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接灿烂的和平之光"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}